I have to share with you.

06:17.344 --> 06:18.343
Okay, sure.

06:18.345 --> 06:19.544
I'll come by
around that part

06:19.546 --> 06:20.979
of the day when
the sun goes away

06:20.981 --> 06:22.514
and we're all terrified
it will never come back.

06:22.516 --> 06:24.649
Okay, bye.

06:24.651 --> 06:26.318
Wow, you're a
lucky man, Joseph.

06:26.320 --> 06:27.352
I know.

06:27.354 --> 06:29.254
So, what have you
got going on later?

06:29.256 --> 06:31.356
I think I might hang
out in the town square.

06:31.358 --> 06:33.492
I hear an oracle from Greece
is sending a funny message

06:33.494 --> 06:35.494
and I want to be
there when it arrives.

06:44.003 --> 06:46.071
(panting)

06:49.442 --> 06:51.943
Penis.
Ha.

06:55.848 --> 06:57.282
Hey, Mary.

06:57.284 --> 06:58.617
Oh, hi, Joseph.
Come on in.

06:58.619 --> 07:00.352
Thanks, hey, listen
I just got tickets

07:00.354 --> 07:01.686
to see Cher in Bethlehem.

07:01.688 --> 07:02.854
You want to go?

07:02.856 --> 07:05.223
I guess-- how close
are the seats?

07:05.225 --> 07:06.291
Row L-X-V-I.

07:06.293 --> 07:07.859
That sounds great.

07:07.861 --> 07:11.062
But, look, Joseph, there's
something I have to tell you.

07:11.064 --> 07:12.364
I'm pregnant.

07:12.366 --> 07:13.532
From my finger?

07:13.534 --> 07:15.100
No, you don't understand.

07:15.102 --> 07:17.602
God has blessed me
with his child.

07:17.604 --> 07:20.372
You banged Kevin God
from South Nazareth?

07:20.374 --> 07:22.941
No, no, Joseph,
I mean God.

07:22.943 --> 07:25.210
I'm carrying God's baby.

07:25.212 --> 07:27.546
He-he sent down an angel.

07:34.387 --> 07:35.387
(gasps)

07:35.389 --> 07:36.555
Fear not, pretty lady

07:36.557 --> 07:38.723
who ain't never
had no relations.

07:38.725 --> 07:41.460
I's been sent to bring you
the message that tonight

07:41.462 --> 07:44.296
you's gonna be getting
pregnant with the Son of God.

07:44.298 --> 07:46.331
It's a miracle, yay!

07:46.333 --> 07:47.599
I am?

07:47.601 --> 07:49.468
Yeah, and it's gonna
be here soon,

07:49.470 --> 07:51.269
so you might want
to spruce yourself up.

07:51.271 --> 07:53.171
Maybe walk in the
creek a little bit.

07:53.173 --> 07:55.607
Oh, and he probably don't
want me to tell you this,

07:55.609 --> 07:57.576
but be ready 'cause
he might give you

07:57.578 --> 07:59.411
a little bit of
a donkey punch.

07:59.413 --> 08:01.513
So you're saying God
got you pregnant?

08:01.515 --> 08:04.483
Yes, Joseph.
Glory in the highest!

08:04.485 --> 08:06.818
Well, if it his will,
then his will be done,

08:06.820 --> 08:08.587
and I am but his
humble servant.

08:08.589 --> 08:09.754
But I do have one question.

08:09.756 --> 08:10.989
Was he bigger than me?

08:10.991 --> 08:12.624
Joseph,
it wasn't like that.

08:12.626 --> 08:14.693
I felt nothing.

08:14.695 --> 08:16.595
Oh, little guy.

08:21.100 --> 08:23.969
ANNOUNCER:
<i>We now return</i>
<i>to</i> A Christmas Carol.

08:23.971 --> 08:25.837
(wind blows)

08:25.839 --> 08:28.773
I am the Ghost
of Christmas Past.

08:28.775 --> 08:30.609
Oh, hello.

08:30.611 --> 08:33.712
I am here to show you
how you lost your way.

08:33.714 --> 08:35.480
Um, oh, okay.

08:35.482 --> 08:37.282
How long is this gonna take?

08:37.284 --> 08:39.985
I don't know,
maybe eight minutes?

08:39.987 --> 08:43.388
Okay, hang on, I just
got to use the bathroom.

08:44.724 --> 08:46.791
(urinating)

08:56.302 --> 08:58.403
(urinating
continues)

09:15.721 --> 09:17.822
(urinating
continues)

