09:32.271 --> 09:34.406
(urinating
continues)

09:40.446 --> 09:43.181
I am the Ghost
of Christmas Pres...

09:43.183 --> 09:46.017
Wait, you haven't
gone yet?
No.

09:46.019 --> 09:48.253
(urinating stops)
Okay, here we go.

09:48.255 --> 09:51.790
(farts)
