into something else.

09:51.792 --> 09:53.858
All right, kids,
gather around.

09:53.860 --> 09:56.728
Time to make our yearly terrible
call to Great Aunt Helen.

09:56.730 --> 09:59.130
(buttons beep)

09:59.132 --> 10:00.298
(phone rings)

10:00.300 --> 10:02.200
HELEN:
Hello?

10:02.202 --> 10:06.171
Hi, Aunt Helen, it's Peter,
Lois and the whole family.

10:07.907 --> 10:10.008
