We're calling to say
Merry Christmas...

10:12.144 --> 10:14.813
Are you there, dear?
We-we were just
calling to...

10:16.282 --> 10:18.383
We had quite a cold snap here.
I hope you
got our card.

10:18.385 --> 10:20.485
Okay, nobody talk-- we'll
just wait for her to talk.

10:25.124 --> 10:27.058
Are you still there, dear?
Well, we just
wanted to...

10:27.060 --> 10:28.994
Damn it!

10:28.996 --> 10:30.962
So, how was the...
It's been rather cold.

10:30.964 --> 10:33.965
The pond froze over
a family of raccoons.

10:36.135 --> 10:37.969
Are you there, dear?
All right, well,
Merry Christmas.

10:37.971 --> 10:41.573
Dad, can we hear more of that
story about the baby Jesus?

10:41.575 --> 10:43.775
Ah, right. Now
everybody listen up

10:43.777 --> 10:46.611
