rhetoric down your throats.

10:46.613 --> 10:47.912
Now, if you remember,

10:47.914 --> 10:51.383
Mary and Joseph were on
their way to Bethlehem.

10:53.352 --> 10:55.487
Uch, look at that.

10:55.489 --> 10:57.088
I remember when this
was all desert.

10:57.090 --> 10:58.289
You know, when
the baby comes,

10:58.291 --> 10:59.924
we could probably
homeschool him.

10:59.926 --> 11:02.293
I can count up to nine.

11:02.295 --> 11:04.329
Yeah, hey, so tell me
one more time how it is

11:04.331 --> 11:05.664
that God got you pregnant.

11:05.666 --> 11:07.132
'Cause when <i>you</i> tell me
the story,

11:07.134 --> 11:08.266
