11:11.371 --> 11:14.005
So, you guys are going
to Bethlehem, huh?

11:14.007 --> 11:16.274
I went there one time on
a donkeys' night out.

11:16.276 --> 11:19.644
Oh, my God,
I got <i>so</i> hammered!

11:19.646 --> 11:23.348
(electrical whirring)

11:23.350 --> 11:26.818
PETER:
<i>And as Mary and Joseph made</i>
<i>their way to Bethlehem,</i>

11:26.820 --> 11:30.388
